java.lang.Object

      de.dfki.lt.signalproc.util.MaryRandomAccessFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.io.DataInput, java.io.DataOutput
public final class MaryRandomAccessFile
extends java.io.RandomAccessFile

Author:
oytun.turk A class that extends RandomAccessFile to read/write arrays of different types while allowing random access to a binary file (i.e. the file can be opened in both read/write mode and there is support for moving the file pointer to any location as required
